name: Matt Weaver
tweet: The pound-for-pound best SLM race you'll see on any given year is the Redbud 400 in Anderson IN. 30ish stock cars on a high-banked quarter-mile and the entry list is excellent each summer.   The Martinsville LMSC 300 is an unreal spectacle. The CARS Tour Throwback 276 is spcial.
